## Blaze syntax demonstration

## Declare functions first
declare/
    |greet| <>
    |add| <>
\

## Define functions
|greet| <
    print/Hello\
    print/World\
:>

|add| <
    var.v-sum-[15]
    print/sum\
:>

## Main program
var.v-old_style-[100]
var.new_style-x-[200]
var.c-PI-[3]

print/old_style\
print/new_style\
print/PI\

^greet/
^add/

## Action block example
do/
    print/999\
\